Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for the traffic light!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something interesting's bound to happen this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will end up crying, and who will be left laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:38.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:44.81,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:50.94,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:56.91,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:01:04.29,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:09.00,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:14.92,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:23.81,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:28.73,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:35.86,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:42.62,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:38.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:44.81,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:50.94,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:56.91,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:01:04.29,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:09.00,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:14.92,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:23.81,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:28.73,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:35.86,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:42.62,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:57.47,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,900)\fscx113.75\fscy102.5\pos(159,377)}Episode 16 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to make it any smaller than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter. It's going into the bonfire anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really gonna light it all on fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take back what I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I said on the day of the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't say things like "no matter what happens, we'll always be friends".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, there's no one who could replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to try my hardest to keep our friendship intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I must like you or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the real "confession time", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better make sure you don't forget those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell?! What are you guys doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.87,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.75,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and tie him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hate us for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hate you for this? Moto! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I'd try my hardest to keep our friendship intact, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If everything goes well between me and Takahashi, everything will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm not going to let you confess to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best way to do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Once I'm all finished, I'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love you, Take-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, carry him over to the science room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want this kind of confession!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just turned on the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the time for confessions this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, look over there! He's confessing to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we getting married out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only say this once, so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I remember, my heart beats so fast... as if it happened only yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana. Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm helping out at the announcement booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you ask something like that right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The announcement booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her I'll be right there, so stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano just left, headed your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my intuition's correct, Takeuchi-kun's coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think hard about it and give them an answer, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them are coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Takahashi here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She was just here a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran away, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I couldn't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not sure about my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They locked me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good... I'm too much of a coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too gutless to actually break the glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he could shatter it without a second thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own way of doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can drop down onto the roof of that storage shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I screw up... I'll come back as a ghost and haunt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... too much of a coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi... Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot pick up the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you even...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it! I won't forgive you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to her first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die before I let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting over her is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't want to talk to anyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She... wanted me to pass that along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just means she doesn't want to hear us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty much her answer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is up with that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't want to hear us out, she should tell us to our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she wants to refuse us, she should say so herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try to understand Nana's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I can sort of understand how Yano feels, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Do you know how to forget about an old love?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You find a new love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that new love is true, then the old love will naturally become part of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is... true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not being fair, running away like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't come up with an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's best... what's most right...\N Will I be able to get through this without crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I think about it, I just don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be hurt anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt anyone, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone wants to hurt anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think the person... or people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you don't want to hurt are probably ready for it if it turns out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, no one wants to make you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... in the end, if it has to be that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those other people are the ones who are wrong, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stay hidden like this tonight, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... can I say one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:14:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi... no one knows what's the best, or what the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you actually see the results, no one ever knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So at the very least, why don't we rely on what we do know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep the feelings we have right now precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings I have right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...return to those days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your answer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, no one wants to make you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you came for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have something you wanted to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like... didn't you have another reason to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moto and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd say that... but anyway, hurry and go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being really sulky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both... so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to answer you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you as much love as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching you, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always watching you, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always watching over you, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, you big liar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I get hurt by him, and I run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I chase after him again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we keep falling in love with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I thought you'd be crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying, damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always annoyed me from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say your own selfish things, and you stir up all my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so clingy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but then you leave me and go away so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet despite all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You annoy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I wish I could rewrite my past."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But I can't."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's impossible."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of present will make your past pale in comparison?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reality where I exist and you're there next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to become stronger...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me all about Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't pressed the issue so far because I've been thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear about your feelings for her, and once I sort out my feelings about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think I might be able to keep going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be difficult for you, but... I think it's necessary for this to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you tell me about Nana-san with your own words from your own mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do that, I can't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see the meaning in doing something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you just run away from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you would. There's no way you could confront it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you've been running from it for two whole years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I couldn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do feel like talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do it, and do it well, I'll give you this as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell me you erased it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you over and over, but you kept telling me you didn't have it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was obviously lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're a little naive yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't try to pull you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to say that now that Takahashi's serious, you'd better get serious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you only take a half-assed attitude towards this, you have no right to make up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, you didn't confess to her at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when she so clearly knows who her heart wants to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going about this in such a roundabout way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long I'm going out with Yano, we'll eventually run into this problem again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll be able to talk about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of interested to know how he feels in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Takeuchi-kun, would you listen with me to the story about Nana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm really uneasy about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a really nice person, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I just don't know when to give up.
