Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:37.54,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in the way. I waved my hand, but your back is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:49.93,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,already swerving through the crowd of people and sinking into the evening sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:58.61,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I closed my eyes and began to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:10.08,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the words you told me. Only happy memories
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:21.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,are supposed to be there, but I become anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:30.43,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my heart waver so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:43.57,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you about my overflowing feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:56.66,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you, I love you, I love you more than anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:07:03.61,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I am, whatever time it may be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:09.65,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,you're always there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:17.04,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll accept that because
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:21.08,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,these memories won't fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:28.88,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, under the deep sea, the time we had
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:34.89,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will become blue sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:40.68,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wonder if it'll be put to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:47.52,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,like these undying feelings I have right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:52.78,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quivering alone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.29,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,in this bed without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:12.26,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I rolled over, I couldn't see the blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:41.04,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You always loved
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.79,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,looking out at the town
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:50.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,from this room, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:56.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The passing seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:02.93,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,were gentle to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:09.19,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Things got awkward, and we became unable to speak to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:15.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and you returned to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:23.83,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel that you're still
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.67,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,living the closest to me, with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:36.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,When I accept the loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:41.14,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I try to leave it to someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:47.02,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's a little easier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:53.65,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Come dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:10:00.32,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in this bed without you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:05.45,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,quivering alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:18.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I close my eyes, I can see the blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:44.35,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, another star shot by in the summer's night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:17:07.00,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,We lovers could feel it in our hearts and upon our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:23.68,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,With just the warmth of your hand holding mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:36.66,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I could go anywhere, fly anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:43.00,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of counting the infinite stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:49.38,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather stay like this with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:57.59,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,forever connected to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:14.86,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I get hurt, or hurt you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:20.07,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:23.41,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:49.85,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you're smiling, and your heart must be beating faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:19:06.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,We're clumsy, and we can't say things very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:30.14,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to keep the feelings we have now precious
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:43.45,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and not wait for them to arrive tomorrow, or have missed them yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:49.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of painting my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:56.71,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather stay like this with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:04.68,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,forever embraced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:16.65,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:23.03,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll strongly leap into my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:28.54,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:33.21,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,but I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:28.53,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A silent rain falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:35.04,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A slightly chilly rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:41.96,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But it continues to fall, without actually hitting me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:49.55,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it's trying to freeze my heart instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:56.10,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always found your gentle back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:04.44,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,on any day, but where do my
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:08.57,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,winding feelings point?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:15.49,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:22.96,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,before you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:29.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep on running
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:36.06,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and we seem like we're going to reach, but don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.85,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,At that distance away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:52.36,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain will fall again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:59.16,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,A slightly lonely rain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:05.63,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will pour all around and spread
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:13.14,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it's meant to soothe my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:19.60,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always looking at your cute back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:28.03,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,but these winding feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.03,0:24:31.95,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,point me in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.95,0:24:39.16,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:46.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,at the end of my search?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:52.88,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep on running
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.88,0:25:00.06,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and we seem like we're going to reach, but don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.06,0:25:02.60,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,At that distance away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.15,0:25:14.78,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,We keep on running
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:21.70,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,and we seem like we're going to reach, but don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.70,0:25:24.50,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,At that distance away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.67,0:25:27.84,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,At that distance away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.04,0:25:31.92,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,At that distance away from you.
