Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.31,0:25:08.57,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I met her in my\N second year of middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.57,0:25:10.32,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she accidentally died in\N the summer of my third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.32,0:25:12.15,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.15,0:25:15.91,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi... are you\N sure it's not Moto...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.91,0:25:18.41,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you who's so\N obsessed with Nana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.41,0:25:21.29,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just forget it...\N There's no helping it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.29,0:25:23.41,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be a normal date.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.41,0:25:27.58,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done\N anything with my dad before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.58,0:25:30.05,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest hurts...
